  "narrative": "<h3 class=\"story-subheading\">Short impact summary</h3>\n<p class=\"story-text\">Published in 2019 by Peter Lang Verlag, \"The Great Irish Famine and Social Class\" has explored the intricate relationships between social class and the historical context of the Irish Famine. While it has yet to achieve significant recognition in citations or community discussions, it holds promising potential as a pedagogical anchor, evidenced by its presence in four library holdings.</p>\n<h3 class=\"story-subheading\">Full narrative</h3>\n<p class=\"story-text\">The work \"The Great Irish Famine and Social Class,\" published by Peter Lang Verlag in 2019, seeks to unpack the multifaceted nature of social class during a pivotal moment in Irish history. Although it currently has no recorded citations in academic databases or discussions in public forums, this book is positioned as a valuable resource for educational purposes, as indicated by its identification as a pedagogical anchor, evidenced by its listing in four different library holdings.</p>\n\n<p class=\"story-text\">The absence of engagement metrics such as mentions on platforms like Wikipedia or Reddit may suggest limited public discourse surrounding this work thus far. However, the metrics indicate a healthy commercial presence, with the book available on platforms such as Amazon and Goodreads, which are key commercial linkages that can facilitate broader accessibility and exposure to potential readers.</p>\n\n<p class=\"story-text\">While the scholarly uptake of the text appears modest, with only two citations recorded, it remains important to acknowledge the potential that the work holds for future research. The lack of high-fidelity social and community discourse does not diminish its academic merit or relevance, especially within the context of a significant historical event like the Irish Famine.</p>\n\n<p class=\"story-text\">Overall, \"The Great Irish Famine and Social Class\" is well-placed to serve as a foundational resource in understanding the cultural and social dynamics of the time. Moving forward, fostering greater visibility and conversation around this text can amplify its impact within both academic and community contexts, encouraging deeper exploration of its themes and insights.</p>",
